         <div type="edition"><ab>
<lb n="1"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">بسم</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">اللّه</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الرّحمن</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الرّحيم</supplied> 
<lb n="2"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">اللّه</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">لا</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">إله</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">إلّا</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">هو</supplied> 
<lb n="3"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الحيّ</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">القيّوم</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">لا</supplied> تأخذ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ه</supplied> 
<lb n="4"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">سنة</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ولا</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">نوم</supplied> له ما في 
<lb n="5"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">السّـ</supplied>ـمو<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ات</supplied> وما في 
<lb n="6"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">الأ</supplied>رض من ذا الّذي 
<lb n="7"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">يشـ</supplied>ـفع عنده إلّا بإذنـ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ـه</supplied> 
<lb n="8"/>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">يعـ</supplied>ـلم ما بين أيديهم 
<lb n="9"/>  وما خلفهم ولا يحيطو 
<lb n="10"/>  ن پسى من علمه 
<lb n="11"/>  بما شا وسع كر 
<lb n="12"/>  سپه 
<lb n="13"/>  والأرض ولا يود<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ه</supplied> 
<lb n="14"/>  حفظهما وهو 
<lb n="15"/>  العلي العظيم فإ 
<lb n="16"/>  ن پولوا ڤڤل 
<lb n="17"/>  اللّه لا إله إلّا هو 
<lb n="18"/>  عليه توكّلت وهو 
<lb n="19"/>  رب العرش 
<lb n="20"/>  لعطپم 
<lb n="21"/>  لا حافظ إلّا اللّه 
</ab></div>
         <div type="edition"><ab>
 <lb n="1"/>bi smi ăl lāhi ăr raḥmāni ăr raḥīmi 
 <lb n="2"/>ăl lāhu lā ʾilāha ʾillā huwa 
 <lb n="3"/>ăl ḥayyu ăl qayyūmu lā taʾḫuḏu hu 
 <lb n="4"/>sinaẗ:un wa lā nawm:un la hu mā fī 
 <lb n="5"/>ăs samāwāti wa mā fī 
 <lb n="6"/>ăl ʾarḍi man ḏā ăllaḏī 
 <lb n="7"/>yašfaʿu ʿinda hu ʾillā bi ʾiḏni hi 
 <lb n="8"/>yaʿlamu mā bayna ʾaydī him 
 <lb n="9"/>wa mā ḫalfa hum wa lā yuḥīṭūna 
 <lb n="10"/>bi šayʾ:in min ʿilmi hi ʾillā 
 <lb n="11"/>bi mā šāʾa wasiʿa kursiyyu hu 
 <lb n="12"/>ăs samāwāti 
 <lb n="13"/>wa ăl ʾarḍa wa lā yaʾūdu hu 
 <lb n="14"/>ḥifẓu humā wa huwa 
 <lb n="15"/>ăl ʿaliyyu ăl ʿaẓīmu fa ʾin 
 <lb n="16"/>tawallaw fa qul ḥasb iya 
 <lb n="17"/>ăl lāhu lā ʾilāha ʾillā huwa 
 <lb n="18"/>ʿalay hi tawakkaltu wa huwa 
 <lb n="19"/>rabbu ăl ʿarši 
 <lb n="20"/>ăl ʿaẓīmi 
 <lb n="21"/>lā ḥāfiẓa ʾillā ăl lāhu 
  </ab></div>
<div type="translation"><ab>
			<lb n="21"/>
		Es gibt keinen Bewahrer außer Gott.
</ab></div>
